Phase 3: Core Customer Features is next. It has 4 steps:

Step	Module	Endpoints	What It Does
9	Storefronts	6	Public tailor profiles, portfolio, reviews display
10	Orders	8	Customer places order, tailor accepts/declines, auto-creates job
11	Reviews	2	Post-delivery reviews, rating aggregation
12	Favourites	3	Save styles, fabrics, tailors
Plus the Marketplace module (styles + fabrics browsing) which Orders and Favourites depend on.

Milestone: Customers can discover tailors, place orders, and leave reviews.

Ready to start Phase 3 Step 9 (Storefronts)?


